\cf3 A song where Luka is supposedly reminscing her childhood, her parents were strict and she was expected to get the highest marks in her class, but there was no time for fun, one day she hears a girl singing from the schools rooftop.\
That girl being Miku, she watches on in amazement as Miku lets herself go and sings to her heart's content before Luka turns away.\
She decides that there's always time for fun and stops berating herself for getting a score lower than 100%, The next day, she goes to the roof and starts to sing, same as she saw Miku doing.\
It's implied that Miku saw her and they were friends ever since.\cf0 \
